Package: quantumPPMS
Type: Package
Title: Analzye Quantum Design PPMS data sets
Version: 0.3.5
Authors@R: person("Thomas", "Gredig", email = "thomas.gredig@csulb.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Thomas Gredig <thomas.gredig@csulb.edu>
Description: Analyze data from Quantum Design Physical Property System (QD-PPMS)
    including the VSM option, analyzes hysteresis loops and extracts sweep
    speeds, coercivity, and saturation magnetization. Some limitations for resistivity
    data and susceptibility data that are not fully supported.
